user.description:
Enter the email and password you use in the PetLibro Lite mobile app. The integration will log in, discover your feeder(s) on the LAN, and pull the local key needed for direct control. The password isn't persisted — it's exchanged for a short-lived session.

LAN IP is optional — leave blank to let the integration auto-discover via UDP broadcast. Fill it in only if your router blocks broadcast or the feeder lives on a different subnet.

